modules.description: This module enables precise handling of UTC timestamps through conversion, parsing, and formatting operations between `Xapi_stdext_date.Date.t`, `Ptime.t`, Unix timestamps (float), and string representations like ISO 8601, RFC 3339, and RFC 822. It supports comparisons (`compare`, `is_earlier`, `diff`) and temporal arithmetic, with use cases including system time conversion, log timestamp validation, and API interactions requiring standardized date formats.

This module handles UTC timestamps with precise conversion, parsing, and formatting between `Date.t`, `Ptime.t`, Unix timestamps, and string formats like ISO 8601. It supports comparisons, temporal arithmetic, and is used for system time conversion, log validation, and API interactions requiring standardized date formats.
